'''Crème D'Infame''' was one of the most sought-after types of [[Wine/Legends|wine]] in the [[The galaxy/Legends|galaxy]]. It was produced during the days of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] through the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]].

